           move      07                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      30                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      rr-cod-age           to   v-num                  .
